## Credit Model

| Action | Credit Cost |
|---|---|
| Research (per brief) | 20 credits |
| Interview (per minute) | 10 credits |
| Content generation (per piece) | 50 credits |
| Section regeneration (Edit phase) | 50 credits |
| Bulk export (per 5 pieces) | 10 credits |

Plans provide monthly credit allocation. Unused credits roll over one month.

