## Multi-Language Support

- `interviewerLanguage` drives STT model language config (Deepgram supports 30+ languages)
- `interviewerLanguage` also drives TTS voice selection (ElevenLabs Multilingual v2 for non-English)
- `outputLanguage` is written explicitly into the Claude system prompt
- The two can differ — cross-language workflows are first-class
- UI defaults to English; Norwegian prioritised as secondary

